\pc \bd 235\bd*

\s Yesu ni Rafiki yetu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu ni Rafiki yetu anayenipenda kweli, Tunaweza kumwambia mahitaji yetu yote. Siku nyingi tunabeba taabu na huzuni kubwa. Kwa sababu tunaacha kumwambia kila neno.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Tunapata majaribu na masikitiko sana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tusishinde na huzuni, twende kumwambia Bwana Kweli hatuna rafiki kama Yesu Musaidia Anayefahamu kwamba sisi ni zaifu sana.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Tunachoka na uzito wa makosa sikuzote\bd*\bd ?\bd*\bd  Bwana Yesu ni Mwokozi, atatupokea wote. Watu wanatuchukia\bd*\bd ?\bd*\bd  Twende kumwambia Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Yeye atatufariji, atachunga na mapendo.\bd*
